ce by the lounge that you can pick up coffee for $3.00 in the morning, since there isn't alot of places in the immediate area.I really did not get a chance to explore the hotel itself, but the decor was very classic, neutral and calming. Also, this is a good hotel if you are seeing a show at The Fillmore as it is literally 3 blocks away.	
